    <item>
        <title>Our Story</title>
        <link>https://example.com/our-story/</link>
        <pubDate>Mon, 20 Apr 2026 10:00:02 +0000</pubDate>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
        <guid isPermaLink="false">https://example.com/?page_id=102</guid>
        <description></description>
        <content:encoded><![CDATA[
<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2>Origin</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->
<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Syl Barista began with one premise: specialty coffee deserves an environment as intentional as the brew itself. From bean sourcing to bar flow, every detail is engineered for consistency and calm.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->
<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2>Craft</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->
<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Our team calibrates extraction, temperature, and milk structure throughout the day to preserve flavor accuracy. We treat hospitality as craft: precise, attentive, and never rushed.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->
<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2>Experience</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->
<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Whether you arrive for a focused work session, a client conversation, or a slow evening, Syl Barista is designed to hold the right pace for every guest.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->
        ]]></content:encoded>
